  <h2>May I Recommend</h3>
  <p>May I Recommend is a fortnightly newsletter about things I think are good. Each newsletter consists of an essay (approximately 500 words or less), some recommended pairings to accompany the essay, and a Thing of the Week. It is inspired by Robin Sloan’s Year of the Meteor, the podcast Wonderful, and my own irrepressible urge to tell people about the stuff I like. Season 1 of the newsletter has been picked up for a one-year run of 26 episodes. No word currently on whether or not there will be a Season 2.</p>
